In a new diagram below, we have $\cos \angle XPY = \frac{3}{5}$. A point Z is placed such that $\angle XPZ$ is a right angle. What is $\sin \angle YPZ$?

[asy]
pair X, P, Y, Z;
P = (0,0);
X = Rotate(-aCos(3/5))*(-2,0);
Y = (2,0);
Z = Rotate(-90)*(2,0);
dot("$Z$", Z, S);
dot("$Y$", Y, S);
