Find the area of triangle $DEF$ below, where $DF = 8$ and $\angle D = 45^\circ$.

[asy]
unitsize(1inch);
pair D,E,F;
D = (0,0);
E= (sqrt(2),0);
F = (0,sqrt(2));
draw (D--E--F--D,linewidth(0.9));
draw(rightanglemark(E,D,F,3));
