(1) Find the rectangular coordinate equation of curve $C$ and the ordinary equation of line $l$ when $\alpha=\frac{\pi}{2}$;

(2) Suppose curve $C$ intersects line $l$ at points $A$ and $B$, and point $P$ has coordinates $(1,2)$. Find the minimum value of $|PA|+|PB|$.

